{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And towards end of the day almost, they finally marched us into-- into one of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When we go in, that barrack had no bed, no-- no furniture, nothing except the bare floor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And from the rain, it was like mud all over the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I said to my sister, how can we sleep in here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean there's no straw, no blanket, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, if we're going to lay down on this mud, we're going to get cholera, because this is ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And finally, we were standing [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They lined us up five in a-- at that time, I didn't know what was [NON-ENGLISH], five in a row.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they were giving some kind of a soup.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And some-- it looked like a-- a gray earthen brick, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They make the brick from earth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So we are waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then we get nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So my sister was so thirsty and-- and so tired, she says to one of the woman, please, have mercy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Give me a-- a [INAUDIBLE], because meantime, five people were drinking from one little pot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So one of them said, here, have a taste.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So when my sister had a swallow, she said, my god, she said, what did you give me?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This is worse than the dishwashing water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So she spit it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So the woman said, you graceful this and this, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "How can you be like that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Here I'm sharing it with you and you spit it out?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So then we'd seen that they all get the bread, that gray things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We get nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So we had to ask, how come we are getting nothing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So they said, because you weren't registered and we didn't get any portion for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
